</p>
<p>
For all those students who want to do MBBS from abroad, Bangladesh is considered as one of the best choices, as medical degree is not very hard to gain. Another best part is that the process of admission is very easy as compared to other states.
</p>
<p>
Bangladesh being Neighbour of India, there are many advantages of studying MBBS in Bangladesh which are as follows:
</p>

