 <ul class="list-item-point-thumb-right">
<li>       Bangladesh has top medical colleges in Asia.</li>
<li>       Exams like IELTS & TOEFL are not required.</li>
<li>       Medical Universities charges low MBBS fees in Bangladesh.</li>
<li>       The students can practice medical in Bangladesh, India or any part of the globe after completing medical studies in Bangladesh.</li>
