<div class="content-post">
<h2 class="title">Benefits of Doing MBBS from Bangladesh:</h2>
<p>There are major benefits of studying MBBS in Bangladesh which are as follows:</p>

<ul class="list-item-point-thumb-right">
<li>Socio- Cultural same as India.</li>
<li>        Less finance cost to complete MBBS course in Private Medical college and free seats under SAARC Quota in Government Medical College.</li>
<li>        NMC Approved medical studies outside India under IMA Act 1956.</li>
<li>        Enhancing student skills they are given practical and experiments.</li>
<li>        Students studying in Bangladesh get the opportunity to complete their internship program and then they can work in multinational companies and hospitals.</li>

</ul>
