<div class="content-post">

<h2 class="title">Procedure of Admission & Documents Required:</h2>
<p>For pursuing MBBS from Bangladesh, you must qualify for NEET which is National Eligibility Entrance Exam. There are certain kind of documents required for taking admission to Medical Colleges in Bangladesh which are as follows:</p>
<ul class="list-item-point-thumb-right">
  Passport with Minimum 18 months validity
<li>      Class 10th and 12th passing Certificate & Mark Sheet</li>
<li>      Birth Certificate </li>
<li>      Passport Size Photos </li>
<li>      Official Invitation Letter from Medical University of Bangladesh </li>
<li>      Legalization of all documents from Embassy of Bangladesh</li>
<li>      Bank Reciept of University 1st Year Tuition Fee</li>
<li>      Visa Fees.</li>

</ul>
